name: The Queen's Dreams: Destruction
description:
Hot venomous rain. Bricks and boulders with meteorlike strength strewn here and there.
All good things had to come to an end.
Mother earth called back.
Enough.
Every mineral was to be avenged.
Yet the marine and pond life knew of no ill.
They swam.
They dove.
Flew through the waters nonplussed.
This was not their battle. They would simply wait for the calm and her rage to subside and then swim once again.
